      <body>
         <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
        
		<div n="a" type="textpart" subtype="fragment"><ab>
		<lb n="1"/><milestone unit="block"/><g ref="#cross"/> <w lemma="ἐκ">ἐκ</w> <persName key="Mary" type="divine"><name>Μαρίης</name></persName> <w lemma="θεόπαις">θεοπαῖδος</w> <w lemma="ἀπηνής">ἀπηνέος</w> <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
		</ab></div><div n="b" type="textpart" subtype="fragment"><ab><lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/> <w lemma="θεοδέγμων">θεοδέγμονα</w> <w lemma="κῆπος">κῆπον</w> <space dim="horizontal"/><milestone unit="block"/></ab></div><div n="c" type="textpart" subtype="fragment"><ab><lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/><orig n="unresolved">νι</orig> <w lemma="τίθημι">θῆκα</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τὸ</w> <w lemma="δῶμα">δῶμα</w> <g ref="#cross"/><milestone unit="block"/></ab></div>
      </div>
         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>b. Reinach read <foreign xml:lang="grc">ΘΕΟΔΕΙΜΟΝΑ</foreign> which was correctly emended by Grégoire.</p>
            <p>c. <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἀνεθήκατο</foreign> Grégoire; <foreign xml:lang="grc">
                  <seg type="damage">
                     <supplied reason="lost">ἀ</supplied>
                  </seg>νίθηκα τὸ</foreign> ALA ed. 1; <foreign xml:lang="grc">
                  <w>
                     <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
                     <orig n="unresolved">νι</orig>
                  </w> θῆκα τὸ</foreign> Feissel (1991); <foreign xml:lang="grc">θήκατο</foreign> Feissel (2002).</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>
		a. From Mary, whose child was God, of harsh <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
            </p>
            <p>b. <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/> the God-receiving garden
		</p>
            <p>c. <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/> I set the house.
		</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>See discussion at <ref type="eAla-text" n="VII.16" target=".xml"/>.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="bibliography">
